  "body": "When running testnets it is desirable to set a wacky `Fork` version to avoid signature collisions when we go to mainnet.\r\n\r\nPresently there's no way to express this in the [configs](https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/tree/dev/configs), which is a little awkward for testnet interop.\r\n\r\nIf we could expose it as a \"constant\" then it would fit nicely into a config.",
